about the best of humanity.</i>

566
00:40:29.552 --> 00:40:31.679
What do you say we rebuild this place?

567
00:40:32.263 --> 00:40:33.263
Need a hand?

568
00:40:33.889 --> 00:40:38.102
<i>♪ Burning in your fireplace
I hear your voice and it seems ♪</i>

569
