Hey. can you help her down there?

608
00:42:54.947 --> 00:42:57.575
<i>♪ Can we go on ♪</i>

609
00:42:57.658 --> 00:43:03.706
<i>♪ Like it once was ♪</i>

610
00:43:04.790 --> 00:43:07.459
